{"tid":1171255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美禁令後財務撐不住了？ 華為首度尋求籌資10億美元","createTime":"2019-05-25T14:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T20:00:05.000Z","uid":75656,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2adc7f12f5e36d5ed5e2b02d3294c575e4d5b1cd","tid":1171255,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:47:31.000Z","msg":"〔編譯楊芙宜／台北報導〕彭博引述知情人士稱，華為遭美國列入貿易黑名單後，首次尋求大規模融資，華為向一些銀行尋求美元或港元離岸貸款，總額約10億美元（約315億台幣），還款期限為5年及7年。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，華為目前和一些銀行的談判處於初步階段，不能確保一定達成協議；如果取得銀行貸款，貸款的定價及參與銀行的身分，可為華為的財政實力提供一些參考。<br />\n<br />\n在美國祭出出口管制的禁令後，華為開始面臨經營上和財務上的雙重壓力。華為2018年財報顯示，截至去年12月，華為的無擔保銀行貸款總額370億元🇨🇳人民幣🇨🇳（約1702億台幣），其中28億元🇨🇳人民幣🇨🇳（約128.8億台幣）貸款在1年內到期。<br />\n<br />\n華為的現金和約當現金總額約為貸款總額的2.6倍。面對美國封殺，多家企業先後暫停與華為的業務往來，令華為的經營面臨挑戰，其美元債券價格跌至近3個月低點。<br />\n<br />\n亞洲著名債券經理Dhiraj Bajaj也看空華為2026年到期的美元債券。彭博先前報導，消息人士表示，中國政府正考慮幫助華為的一些選項，包括草擬應急方案，必要的話將向其提供財務援助。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2801833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2801833&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFMjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=75b795af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2801833&h=f58bf3a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2801833</a><br />\n彭博link:<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-05-24/huawei-seeks-1-billion-in-first-big-funding-test-after-u-s-ban\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-05-24%2Fhuawei-seeks-1-billion-in-first-big-funding-test-after-u-s-ban&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFMjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=e1d84cd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-05-24/huawei-seeks-1-billion-in-first-big-funding-test-after-u-s-ban</a><br />\n<br />\n10億美金唔多，但佢文入面又話現金係總負債既2.6倍？點解咁急撲水？有冇金融高手解釋下係正常借貸定真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外，如果支共出手咪更加証明佢唔係民企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ea7a98f13be5b04a53c3aa1021b5af2b51723b","tid":1171255,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:50:09.000Z","msg":"要有足夠流動資金先可以向銀行繼續借錢"},{"pid":"bf16ff81e9604a567433b5b3cf8efeb9a8907acb","tid":1171255,"uid":4811,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"做手機套，11億人一人買一個都大把世界"},{"pid":"ac1553eebf1b7f9c1e99967e4059e86d5fff2865","tid":1171255,"uid":13663,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:52:12.000Z","msg":"共產黨唔係無限金錢咩<br />\n做咩要問香港銀行借錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c287ee788116e063f2b66fe4cfce07d6c14b941","tid":1171255,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"東亞銀行又係時候做白手套"},{"pid":"67fd312c8f193fac33be12954d708a0e26baf6b9","tid":1171255,"uid":68620,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"做得好，華維最好快d消失"},{"pid":"0ff6d59e773c3d380a7784da28d75eddd6c9f198","tid":1171255,"uid":13663,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"1c287ee788116e063f2b66fe4cfce07d6c14b941","tid":1171255,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"東亞銀行又係時候做白手套"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"邊間借 真係要提錢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b412d1c619dbfdaffd72a68fe43d6bbcb26f5b","tid":1171255,"uid":160605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"又話d蝗蟲愛國，依家去掃晒華為d貨幫佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd72cbe80cf80514955a7b2b9750a7d08a2647ad","tid":1171255,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201